    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Here&#39;s the thing.  In that tiny crevice, in the back corners of your mind (where the cobwebs are), you know you&#39;ll get there.  A work is never &#8220;done,&#8221; at some point it just becomes finished.  The self loathing is just a little loud right now.  (Or perhaps that&#39;s just me when I write.  Anyone?!)  </p>
<p>I love when you post about writing as much as I do when you post about food. As Ms. Lamott would say, turn radio station KFKD down.</p>
