      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn">Heidi</cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/12/in-my-better-moments/#comment-36122"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-12-15T13:26:59-05:00">Thursday, December 15, 2011 at 1:26 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Molly, your writing is your truest gift.  The finished work will be wonderful, it cannot help but be so. Like all creative people, you&#39;re hearing the annoying inner critic whisper in your ear. Sometimes you just have to tell it to shut up and go away!</p>
    </div>

