      <p>What you really need to read is Annie Lamont and her comment in &#8220;Bird by Bird&#8221; &#8211; &#8220;Now, practically even better news than that of short assignments is the idea of shitty first drafts. All good writers write them. This is how they end up with good second drafts and terrific third drafts.&#8221;</p>
