  <li id="comment-36335" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="http://www.twentyeightletters.com" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">beth</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/12/in-my-better-moments/#comment-36335"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-12-16T08:08:10-05:00">Friday, December 16, 2011 at 8:08 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I have been away for a while, and I have a whole pile of drafts to return to. I thought it would be good to have some space from them. One the one hand, returning to them feel more than a little daunting. On the other, it is nice to know how what I will be doing when I imagine the new year.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
      <a rel='nofollow' class='comment-reply-link' href='#comment-36335' data-commentid="36335" data-postid="455" data-belowelement="comment-36335" data-respondelement="respond" data-replyto="Reply to beth" aria-label='Reply to beth'>Reply</a>    </div>
