      <p>You actually aren&#39;t worrying &#8211; you are contemplating, thinking, hatching, editing &#8212; all in the back of your mind, while feeling that you can&#39;t complete it.  But obviously you can.  You have done it before, and you can do it again; you just have to get through this blasted portion of the process.  I have faith!</p>
