  <li id="comment-36345" class="comment odd alt thread-odd thread-alt depth-1">
    <header class="comment--meta">
      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/08504650716282984100" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Diana vW</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/12/in-my-better-moments/#comment-36345"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-12-16T23:34:47-05:00">Friday, December 16, 2011 at 11:34 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>If you are ever inclined, a cruise ship with a lot of sea days in a row is the ideal place to write.  A repositioning cruise is very reasonable.  Great food and pampering and uninterrupted time with no clutter or obligations.  My husband and I just finished a book between Portugal and Miami.  </p>
<p>You inspire me!</p>
    </div>

