      <p>Many, many thanks for the kind comments, friends.   I know I&#39;ll be rereading them over and over in these next weeks and months.  You make me feel much better.</p>
<p>And to those who mentioned Anne Lamott and shitty first drafts, absolutely!  I&#39;ve read <i>Bird by Bird</i> three times.  Still not very comfortable with just how shitty those drafts can be, though.  I&#39;m working on that&#8230;</p>
