      <div class="vcard"><cite class="comment-author fn"><a href="https://www.blogger.com/profile/01493708300940204826" class="url" rel="ugc external nofollow">Molly</a></cite></div>
      <a href="https://orangette.net/2011/12/in-my-better-moments/#comment-36366"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2011-12-19T02:24:02-05:00">Monday, December 19, 2011 at 2:24 am</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Many, many thanks for the kind comments, friends.   I know I&#39;ll be rereading them over and over in these next weeks and months.  You make me feel much better.</p>
<p>And to those who mentioned Anne Lamott and shitty first drafts, absolutely!  I&#39;ve read <i>Bird by Bird</i> three times.  Still not very comfortable with just how shitty those drafts can be, though.  I&#39;m working on that&#8230;</p>
<p>And kale @ tastes good to me, yes, there was indeed Campari in there!  But I can&#39;t remember whether it was a Negroni or an Americano.  Probably a Negroni.</p>
    </div>

