    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>its so funny being on the other side. as a reader, i just see a talented author with stories i&#39;m drawn into.  when i finished a homemade life, i was sorry it ended.  thankfully you work through the challenges of being a writer, so we can all enjoy the fruits of your labor. not everyone has courage to pursue dreams and put aside fear of rejection or failure, as you do</p>
    </div>

