    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Please don&#39;t poke your eye out. <br />I can&#39;t imagine you ever writing a single bad word. As I first began to fall in love with writing you were such a great source of inspiration. You were the one who told me to read Bird by Bird, a favorite to this day, and you were the one who encouraged the very rough, rough draft. I&#39;ve never thanked you for your time and encouragement. Thank you.<br />I wish I could offer you the same type of encouragement by I&#39;m afraid my words fail. <br />Just keep going, bird by bird. And if you need a break for a cookie, I am your girl.</p>
    </div>

